1
00:00:14,940 --> 00:00:15,420
Martial Uncle,

2
00:00:15,940 --> 00:00:17,620
Yaoyang and that woman...

3
00:00:18,100 --> 00:00:19,020
Yaoyang,

4
00:00:19,740 --> 00:00:21,580
what have you done?

5
00:00:26,220 --> 00:00:27,980
That woman just now looked like

6
00:00:28,740 --> 00:00:29,620
Immortal Xiyin.

7
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:31,260
But why does she

8
00:00:31,620 --> 00:00:33,340
carry the fiendish aura of Xieyun?

9
00:00:37,420 --> 00:00:38,540
We lost the Fushi Mirror

10
00:00:39,100 --> 00:00:40,220
and let Yaoyang escape.

11
00:00:40,740 --> 00:00:42,300
If the Immortal Venerable finds out
about this,

12
00:00:42,420 --> 00:00:43,980
who knows how many strikes of
heavenly thunder we'll have to endure.

13
00:00:44,660 --> 00:00:45,940
If you value your lives,

14
00:00:46,260 --> 00:00:47,420
keep your mouths shut.

15
00:00:47,740 --> 00:00:48,220
Yes.

16
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:51,680
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 15]

17
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:42,660
I drew this!

18
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,580
This is you.

19
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:45,380
This is me.

20
00:02:06,180 --> 00:02:06,980
Master.

21
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:09,380
Look.

22
00:02:09,940 --> 00:02:10,740
This is you.

23
00:02:11,180 --> 00:02:11,980
This is me.

24
00:02:14,780 --> 00:02:16,580
I asked you to copy the immortal arts,

25
00:02:16,940 --> 00:02:18,180
and here you are carving figures.

26
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:19,780
You'll be punished

27
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:21,260
by copying the mantra
ten thousand times.

28
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:22,820
If you don't finish by tonight,

29
00:02:23,020 --> 00:02:23,940
no dinner for you.

30
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:35,540
You can't just scribble on clothes
like that.

31
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:38,020
Since you dirtied the clothes,

32
00:02:38,380 --> 00:02:39,820
you'll be punished
by washing them clean.

33
00:02:40,580 --> 00:02:41,620
If you don't finish by tonight,

34
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:42,780
no dinner for you.

35
00:02:51,460 --> 00:02:52,620
My little figures.

36
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:32,260
It's getting late.

37
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:33,460
Time to sleep.

38
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:37,100
I...

39
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:38,620
What is it?

40
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:40,540
The bed is too hard.

41
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:42,260
I can't sleep.

42
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:44,140
Sleeping on a hard bed

43
00:04:44,660 --> 00:04:46,340
helps with your cultivation
of immortal arts.

44
00:04:49,020 --> 00:04:49,820
I...

45
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:50,820
What now?

46
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:53,940
Can I not cultivate?

47
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:55,060
No.

48
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:25,140
What...

49
00:05:26,020 --> 00:05:26,820
What are you doing?

50
00:05:27,260 --> 00:05:28,260
Get up.

51
00:05:28,980 --> 00:05:30,060
I'm sleepy.

52
00:05:32,300 --> 00:05:33,260
Men and women should maintain propriety.

53
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:34,620
What would people think

54
00:05:34,940 --> 00:05:35,780
if we shared a bed?

55
00:05:38,660 --> 00:05:39,500
I'm sleepy.

56
00:06:30,420 --> 00:06:31,780
Don't do that again.

57
00:06:34,260 --> 00:06:35,140
Stingy.

58
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:37,860
Do you understand that men and women
should maintain propriety?

59
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:40,180
Kiss?

60
00:06:44,220 --> 00:06:45,020
I get it.

61
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:49,700
What are you doing?

62
00:06:50,180 --> 00:06:51,340
You said

63
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:52,780
"kiss".

64
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:55,460
Men and women shouldn't get too close,

65
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:56,780
kiss casually,

66
00:06:57,260 --> 00:06:58,740
or share a bed.

67
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:00,740
Only married couples
can do these things.

68
00:07:01,340 --> 00:07:01,980
Understand?

69
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:06,940
Then

70
00:07:07,300 --> 00:07:08,020
let's get married.

71
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:08,820
No!

72
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:11,100
Why?

73
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:12,420
No reason.

74
00:07:15,740 --> 00:07:16,540
Today,

75
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:18,700
I'll teach you
the Mind-Purifying Mantra.

76
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:23,460
Listen carefully.

77
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:34,820
Mind and spirit as one.

78
00:07:35,940 --> 00:07:37,380
Breath follows its course.

79
00:07:38,060 --> 00:07:39,340
Separate yet connected.

80
00:07:39,940 --> 00:07:41,140
Unshaken by changes.

81
00:07:41,980 --> 00:07:43,180
Immortal and mortal merge.

82
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,380
Purify the mind and focus the spirit.

83
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:48,940
Okay.

84
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:49,900
I'll try.

85
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:54,340
Mind and spirit as one.

86
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,620
Breath follows its course.

87
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:07,860
Is this okay?

88
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:11,820
When Master taught me,

89
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:14,900
it took me a long time to learn.

90
00:08:15,420 --> 00:08:16,540
What is

91
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:18,260
a "master"?

92
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:19,380
A master...

93
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:21,220
A master

94
00:08:23,020 --> 00:08:24,460
is someone who teaches skills.

95
00:08:28,180 --> 00:08:28,980
Alright.

96
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:30,540
One more time.

97
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:36,580
Mind and spirit as one.

98
00:08:37,060 --> 00:08:38,260
Breath follows its course.

99
00:08:38,380 --> 00:08:39,740
Separate yet connected.

100
00:08:39,820 --> 00:08:41,020
Unshaken by changes.

101
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,660
Immortal and mortal merge.

102
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:43,980
Purify the mind and focus the spirit.

103
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,620
Ruoxi, watch out!

104
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:57,420
No more fooling around.

105
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:01,180
Thank you.

106
00:09:02,060 --> 00:09:02,860
Master.

107
00:09:04,220 --> 00:09:05,180
What did you call me?

108
00:09:06,420 --> 00:09:07,220
Master.

109
00:09:10,780 --> 00:09:11,780
I am not your Master.

110
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:13,580
Don't call me that again.

111
00:09:22,900 --> 00:09:23,380
Practicing swordsmanship

112
00:09:23,860 --> 00:09:25,420
is also a key part
of immortal cultivation.

113
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:26,820
Hold your breath and calm your spirit.

114
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,460
Focus.

115
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:13,000
♪What is flickering?♪

116
00:10:13,220 --> 00:10:15,740
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

117
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:21,740
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

118
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:24,620
♪What is falling?♪

119
00:10:25,060 --> 00:10:27,860
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

120
00:10:28,100 --> 00:10:33,300
♪Like enduring too many farewells♪

121
00:10:34,220 --> 00:10:35,820
♪When petals drift down♪

122
00:10:35,860 --> 00:10:37,320
♪When the rain falls all around♪

123
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:40,020
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

124
00:10:40,180 --> 00:10:41,880
♪Beyond the dunes♪

125
00:10:41,980 --> 00:10:43,260
♪No end in sight♪

126
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:46,260
♪I am like a mayfly♪

127
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:47,820
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

128
00:10:47,860 --> 00:10:49,320
♪Nor will I run away♪

129
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:52,280
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

130
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:57,540
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

131
